How to get pod IP?


Quick Comparison

Command                                              Use case
---------------------------------------------------------------------------
kubectl get pod <name> -o wide                       Single pod IP with details
kubectl get pods -o wide                             All pods IP at once
kubectl describe pod <name>                          Full pod details including IP
kubectl get pod <name> -o jsonpath='{.status.podIP}' Only the IP, clean output

